#. Tag: title
#: debugging.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "Debugging"
msgstr "Odpravljanje napak"

#. Tag: title
#: debugging.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting the Debugger"
msgstr "Zagon razhroščevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Debugging support is provided for Assembly, SDCC and Microbe, when they are "
"open as a text document. From here, stepping is controlled via the "
"<guimenu>Debug</guimenu> menu. There are two methods of starting the "
"debugger."
msgstr ""
"Podpora za odpravljanje napak je na voljo za Assembly, SDCC in Microbe, ko "
"so odprti kot besedilni dokument. Od tu se koraki nadzirajo prek menija "
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu>. Obstajata dva načina za zagon "
"razhroščevalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the PIC program is already running in a circuit, then double-clicking on "
"the PIC component will open up the program. For assembly PIC programs, the "
"debugger for that text document will be linked into the PIC component. In "
"this case, the debug menu cannot stop the PIC program - as this is owned by "
"the PIC component."
msgstr ""
"Če se program PIC že izvaja v vezju, bo dvoklik na komponento PIC odprl "
"program. Za programe PIC v zbirniku bo razhroščevalnik za ta besedilni "
"dokument povezan s komponento PIC. V tem primeru meni za odpravljanje napak "
"ne more ustaviti programa PIC - ker je ta v lasti komponente PIC."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the assembly file is already opened, then the debugger can be run via the "
"<guimenu>Debug</guimenu> menu. After compiling the program, the debugger "
"will be ready, with the PIC program paused at the first instruction. Note "
"that when debugging high level languages, the current execution point will "
"not be shown if there is no line that corresponds to the first assembly "
"instruction to be executed. In this case, clicking <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton> will bring the execution point to the first line in the program."
msgstr ""
"Če je datoteka zbirnika že odprta, lahko razhroščevalnik zaženete prek "
"menija <guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu>. Po prevajanju programa bo "
"razhroščevalnik pripravljen, pri čemer bo program PIC zaustavljen ob prvem "
"ukazu. Upoštevajte, da pri odpravljanju napak v visoko nivojskih jezikih "
"trenutna točka izvajanja ne bo prikazana, če ni vrstice, ki bi ustrezala "
"prvemu ukazu zbirnika, ki naj se izvede. V tem primeru bo klik na "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> pripeljal točko izvajanja na prvo vrstico v "
"programu."

#. Tag: title
#: debugging.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "Controlling the Debugger"
msgstr "Krmiljenje razhroščevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The debugger can be in one of two modes: running, and stepping. While "
"running, the PIC program will be simulated in realtime. To allow stepping, "
"the PIC program must be paused - either by clicking on "
"<guimenuitem>Interrupt</guimenuitem> in the <guimenu>Debug</guimenu> menu, "
"or clicking on the pause button on the PIC component."
msgstr ""
"Razhroščevalnik je lahko v enem od dveh načinov: tekočem in koračnem. Med "
"delovanjem bo program PIC simuliran v realnem času. Da omogočite korakanje, "
"je treba program PIC začasno ustaviti - bodisi s klikom na "
"<guimenuitem>Prekinitev</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</"
"guimenu> ali s klikom na gumb za premor na komponenti PIC."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In stepping mode, a green arrow in the margin of the text document indicates "
"the next line to be executed (familiar to <application>KDevelop</"
"application> users). It may be useful to turn on the icon border via the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu (it can be permanently turned on via the "
"<guilabel>Editor Settings</guilabel> dialog)."
msgstr ""
"V koračnem načinu zelena puščica na robu besedilnega dokumenta označuje "
"naslednjo vrstico, ki jo je treba izvesti (znano uporabnikom "
"<application>KDevelop</application>). Morda bo koristno vklopiti obrobo "
"ikone v meniju <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> (lahko jo trajno vklopite v "
"pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Nastavitve urejevalnika</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are three types of stepping:"
msgstr "Obstajajo tri vrste korakov:"

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Step</guimenuitem> - This executes the current instruction. The "
"green arrow is moved onto the next line to be executed."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Korak</guimenuitem> - Ta izvede trenutni ukaz. Zelena puščica "
"se premakne v naslednjo vrstico za izvedbo."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Step Over</guimenuitem> - If the next instruction to be "
"executed is a call, or similar, then this will \"step over\" the call, "
"returning to stepping mode once the call has returned. Otherwise, stepping "
"over an instruction behaves identically to step. To put it technically - the "
"initial stack level is recorded, and the program execution is paused once "
"the stack level returns to its initial level."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prestop</guimenuitem> – Če je naslednji ukaz, ki ga je treba "
"izvesti, klic ali podobno, bo to \"prestopilo\" klic in se vrnilo v način "
"korakanja, ko se klic vrne. V nasprotnem primeru se korak čez navodilo "
"obnaša enako kot korak. Tehnično povedano - začetna raven sklada se zabeleži "
"in izvajanje programa se začasno ustavi, ko se raven sklada vrne na začetno "
"raven."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Step Out</guimenuitem> - If the current execution is inside a "
"call, or similar, then this will wait until the call returns. Similarly to "
"stepping over, this is equivalent to waiting until the stack level returns "
"to one less than the initial level, if the initial level is greater than "
"zero."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izstop</guimenuitem> – Če je trenutna izvedba znotraj klica ali "
"podobno, bo to počakalo, dokler se klic ne vrne. Podobno kot pri prestopanju "
"je to enakovredno čakanju, da se raven sklada vrne na eno nižjo raven od "
"začetne ravni, če je začetna raven večja od nič."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Breakpoints allow the execution to be paused when the PIC program reaches a "
"given instruction. To toggle a breakpoint on the line containing the cursor, "
"either use the <guimenu>Debug</guimenu> menu, or click on the icon border of "
"the text document."
msgstr ""
"Prekinitvene točke omogočajo zaustavitev izvajanja, ko program PIC doseže "
"dani ukaz. Če želite preklopiti prekinitveno točko v vrstici, ki vsebuje "
"kazalec, uporabite meni <guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu> ali kliknite "
"na rob ikone besedilnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: debugging.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Symbol Viewer</guilabel> sidebar on the right shows the values "
"of the Special Function Registers. To find out the value of a variable in "
"the General Purpose Registers, you can hover your mouse over the variable "
"name in an instruction that operates on that register. Note that the radix "
"selection in the <guilabel>Symbol Viewer</guilabel> also controls how the "
"value is displayed when hovering over a variable."
msgstr ""
"Stranska vrstica <guilabel>Pregledovalnik simbolov</guilabel> na desni "
"prikazuje vrednosti registrov posebnih funkcij. Če želite ugotoviti vrednost "
"spremenljivke v registrih splošnega namena, lahko z miško premaknete nad ime "
"spremenljivke v navodilu, ki deluje na tem registru. Upoštevajte, da izbira "
"korena v <guilabel>Pregledovalniku simbolov</guilabel> nadzoruje tudi, kako "
"je vrednost prikazana, ko miškin kazalec premaknete nad spremenljivko."
